<div style="text-align: justify;">
<p><strong>The object, a piece of handwritten musical score entitled <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-012">&quot;On Mount Golgotha&quot;</a>, part of a larger set of sheet music, appears to be incomplete. The red/black ink, first thought to be some form of berry or natural dye ink, was later found to be human blood from multiple subjects.</strong></p>
